{"tid":789081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊個做嘅？】「請勿抓幼蟬來吃」 日本公園豎立中英文告示指有人大量捕捉","createTime":"2018-08-22T03:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T09:40:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"62aacd16866ec30636c9433e5f17099080184776","tid":789081,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180822/large/1534901999_d29c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180822%2Flarge%2F1534901999_d29c.jpg&h=16abf135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">公園設置告示板禁止抓蟬的幼蟲來吃(互聯網)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夏蟬唧唧，令人一聽就倍添夏意，不過日本最近似乎有人大量捕捉蟬幼蟲來吃，令公園方面豎立告示牌，引起民眾議論紛紛︰到底是誰這樣做呀？<br />\n<br />\n埼玉縣川口市的青木町公園綜合運動場內，當局設置了告示板，以日文、英文以及中文寫著︰「請不要在公園內抓蟬的幼蟲等生物食用。」據市政府表示，由於收到數名市民投訴，表示有人大量捕捉幼蟬，形容「膠瓶內裝得很滿」，因而最近設置這個告示板，並加上「食用」的字眼。<br />\n<br />\n這塊告示板引來網民熱烈討論，住在運動場附近、每天都來運動的75歲伯伯表示︰「有時會看到小孩抓蟬來玩，但沒看過也沒聽過有人抓來吃的。很好奇誰會吃。」<br />\n<br />\n不過市政府表示，不會限制兒童採集昆蟲等活動，自從設置了告示板後，就沒有再收到民眾投訴了。預計過了蟬鳴時期後，就會把告示板撤掉。<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180822/58592475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180822%2F58592475&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=43bab9d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180822%2F58592475&h=9629f70f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180822/58592475</a>"},{"pid":"c4b47230f6d36376a3ef839b287e620deefd12fd","tid":789081,"uid":32059,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"嬴國人去日本搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0306c05c7710385318ce9cc632ed8c3